    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「精准策略、即时对决，在无情的竞技场中掌控你的AI战队！」</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于这款游戏 (About This Game)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180830/extras/81c78cec305a3c02bcbbb78a156e3fb8.poster.avif?t=1772093378\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180830/extras/81c78cec305a3c02bcbbb78a156e3fb8.webm?t=1772093378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180830/extras/81c78cec305a3c02bcbbb78a156e3fb8.mp4?t=1772093378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《芯链战线》</strong> 是一款融合战略与创造力的竞技策略游戏，专为热爱深度战术思考与创新玩法的玩家设计。在游戏中，你将化身为一位经历末日浩劫后的超级AI，通过程序化你的机器人队伍，展开激烈的资源争夺与策略对决。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>计划你的战略，编写你的命运！</strong><br>运用模块化的芯片系统，打造专属于你的机器人AI，测试并优化它们的行动逻辑，在每场战斗中找出最强策略！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快速迭代，战术至上！</strong><br>Circuit Stance 提供快速而多变的回合制对抗，让你在短时间内体验从实验到极致策略的完整循环。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>竞技场中的胜者为王！</strong><br>游戏采用独特的阶梯式积分系统，每一场胜利都会为你的排名带来飞跃，但失败也将带来挑战。每一场战斗都至关重要！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>风格化的平面动画与未来主题！</strong><br>游戏以扁平化动漫风格呈现，搭配未来感十足的界面与机械设计，为你带来视觉与策略上的双重享受。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >适合谁来玩？ (Who is this game for?)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180830/extras/8c00d0f692f5b0ec09cb3d4d285bd88c.poster.avif?t=1772093378\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180830/extras/8c00d0f692f5b0ec09cb3d4d285bd88c.webm?t=1772093378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180830/extras/8c00d0f692f5b0ec09cb3d4d285bd88c.mp4?t=1772093378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喜欢像 <strong>Backpack Battles</strong>、<strong>Slay the Spire</strong> 的玩家</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >热爱深度策略、优化与快速战术挑战的人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >讨厌时间管理元素，想直接进入策略核心的玩家</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色 (Features)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180830/extras/df6a985a32be4734266e93aa628f8177.poster.avif?t=1772093378\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180830/extras/df6a985a32be4734266e93aa628f8177.webm?t=1772093378\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180830/extras/df6a985a32be4734266e93aa628f8177.mp4?t=1772093378\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>模块化战术编程</strong>：设计并编排你的机器人AI芯片行动，创造多变的战术流派。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>高风险高回报的竞技体验</strong>：每场比赛都能提升你的排名，或者让你面临重新挑战的考验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>循环性的策略测试</strong>：快速完成实验，优化你的战术并在战斗中检验它们的威力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>平面动漫美术风格</strong>：轻量化但充满未来科技感的视觉表现，让每场比赛更加生动。</p></li></ul>",
